Setidaknya kalian
bisa beristirahat.

902
01:57:59,740 --> 01:58:01,360
Kau kelihatan tak asing.

903
01:58:06,610 --> 01:58:08,200
Kau nyaris kehilangan kepala.

904
01:58:11,250 --> 01:58:15,310
Itu kedua kalinya
Anda menyelamatkanku.

905
01:58:18,120 --> 01:58:19,550
Yang pertama...

906
01:58:20,260 --> 01:58:23,890
